snippet.title: Cymaticaly Muffed Campaign Clip
snippet.description:
https://muffed.kelsam.net/steam

Muffed is a top-down shooter with a couch coop adventure campaign for 1-4 players, and a PvP battle arena for 2-16 local players. Fight, sneak, or dash past friends and enemies as you attempt to discover the secrets hidden in this action-packed world. Unleash the power of cymatics!

Credits: https://muffed.kelsam.net/credits/
